  "title": "🌟Bookstore Admin Assistant |$2,200🌟",
  "description": "<p><strong>🌟Bookstore Admin Assistant |$2,200🌟</strong><br /></p><p>📍Location: <strong>VivoCity /Causeway Point / Town</strong></p><p>💰Salary: <strong>$2,000 –$2,200 </strong>\n⏰Working Hours:<strong> Monday - Friday, 10.45am - 8.30pm</strong></p><p><br />Join a dynamic retail team and play a key role in keeping store operations running smoothly! If you’re organised, detail-oriented, and enjoy a fast-paced retail environment, this role is for you.</p><p><br /><strong>\n📝 Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform daily administrative functions for the retail store</li><li>Process SAP-related documents (invoice verification, goods receipt, data entry, filing)</li><li>Handle incoming phone calls and manage office/housekeeping supplies replenishment</li><li>Assist with stocktaking exercises</li><li>Support ad-hoc duties as assigned by the Retail Manager</li></ul><p><br />\n<strong>🎯Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>O Level with <strong>at least 2 years of relevant experience</strong> (retail or hospitality preferred)</li><li><strong>Proficient in MS Office</strong></li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Able to multitask and thrive in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Able to start immediately or within short notice</li><li><strong>No long holiday plans from October to mid-January</strong> (super peak retail period)</li></ul><p><br />\n<strong>📩 Apply Now</strong><br />\nSubmit your resume to</p><p>📧 Email : <a href=\"mailto:annabelle.koh@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">annabelle.koh@crew.sg</a></p><p> 📲 Whatsapp: 80882564</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Annabelle Koh (R25158748)</p><p>Hrnet Ventures Pte Ltd - Crew by Hrnet</p><p>E.A.24C2435</p>",
